Actuators

Spring Boot Actuator is a production-ready feature that provides built-in endpoints to monitor, manage, and observe the health, metrics, and internal state of a Spring Boot application.

It provides built-in endpoints that give insights into your application's:

Health

Metrics

Environment

Beans

Logs

Thread dumps

HTTP traces

